Output session.gif
Set Width 1240
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 15
Set Padding 16
Type "HOME=/tmp/pf-home claude --model claude-opus-4-8 --append-system-prompt 'Live demo over the pineforge MCP. Use its tools for Pine compiling, Binance OHLCV, and backtests. Keep every reply short — a few lines. Do exactly one step per user message; do not run ahead. Write any CSV under /work.'"
Enter
Sleep 14s
Type "hey can you write me a simple breakout trading strategy in pine script — buy when bitcoin breaks above its recent highs? just make sure it compiles for now."
Enter
Sleep 90s
Type "nice — now show me how it would've actually done on real bitcoin prices."
Enter
Sleep 115s
Type "can you try a few different lookback lengths and tell me which one worked best?"
Enter
Sleep 150s
Type "/quit"
Enter
Sleep 2s
